P_Description: The WI-C200 is comfortable, versatile and practical in-ear headphones that will fit seamlessly and stylishly into your life. Whether you’re listening to pop hits, classical concertos or tapping your feet through jazz solos, the headphones delivers dynamic audio performance with deep bass and outstanding clarity. It is time to stop untangling lengthy wires and start enjoying music on the go. Now enjoy non-stop music on the move. With a great battery life up to 15 hours of playback, listen to your favourite playlists and podcasts all through the day. To top it off, headphones come with an upgraded quick charge function. When the battery runs low, just 10 minutes of charging gets you a full 60 minutes of playback. This means that even if you’re in a rush, you’ll soon be ready to get the music going again. Users can go completely hands-free while making calls or listening to music as headphones comes with a built-in microphone and are compatible with Google Assistant and Siri. One can enjoy entertainment on the go, connect with friends, check the weather, listen to music, set reminders, and more, using just your voice. Press the multi-function button twice and you’ll get instant access to Siri or Google Assistant. The impressively light-weight in-ear headphones come with neck-band design to ensure comfort and to keep the headphones out of the way, So the user can listen to music with total freedom. Weighing 15g, the new headphones are engineered perfectly to offer comfortable listening experience and carry around all-day long. Those new headphones will make the music more immersive and enjoyable. With 9mm driver units headphones deliver clear and punchy sound. The compact headphones can be stored effortlessly in a bag. The magnetic housing cleverly snaps the earbuds in place to keep tangled cords at bay. Now charging your device has got a lot simpler. All you need is to connect the device with a Type C cable, and you can charge the battery to full in just three hours. Say goodbye to tangled wires and enjoy flawless, interruption-free listening.

Whether you’re listening to pop hits, classical concertos or tapping your feet through jazz solos, the headphones delivers dynamic audio performance with deep bass and outstanding clarity. Weighing 15g, the new headphones are engineered perfectly to offer comfortable listening experience and carry around all-day long. Those new headphones will make the music more immersive and enjoyable. With 9mm driver units headphones deliver clear and punchy sound. The compact headphones can be stored effortlessly in a bag. The magnetic housing cleverly snaps the earbuds in place to keep tangled cords at bay. Now charging your device has got a lot simpler. Trouble shooting step for Audio problem One of the easier fixes. If you’re only receiving audio through one ear of the headset, make sure the cord is fully plugged into the audio device. If the headset jack is only pushed in halfway, you may receive audio through just one ear or the issue might have occurred due wear and tear use from customer end. If the audio is still only working in one ear, check the headset in a different audio device. This can help you determine whether the headset or the audio device is at fault – and continue on the road to resolution. It may also be worth testing alternate headsets in the audio device to help you arrive at the correct conclusion.

To unpause the music, place the earbud back into your ear within 60 seconds. After 60 seconds (or when mono playback is preferred) the music can be unpaused by pressing the multi-function button.To conserve battery the right earbud will automatically power off when it is out of range of your smartphone for 15 minutes and is not in the charging case or when it has been inactive for 1 hour. The left earbud will automatically power off when it has not had a link with the right earbud for 15 minutes and is not in the charging case.To power the earbuds on, place them in the charging case or hold the multi-function button on the right earbud and/or the volume down button on the left earbud, until the LED flashes.Charging Case, micro USB cable, 3 sets of Silicon EarGels, Quick Start Guide and Warning Leaflets, TA label

P_Description: The WH-XB900N is Wireless Extra Bass and Noise Cancellation Headphones with Quick Attention Mode, Touch Sensor, Sense Engine and Built-In Alexa. Hear e bass and don’t let the noise stop you. Thanks to Digital Noise Cancelling which cuts out ambient noise enabling you to hear more detail in every track. This headphones is designed to deliver powerful, deep and punchy bass response. Equipped with Quick Attention Mode, Headphones enables you to know what’s going on around without taking the headphones off. Simply place your hand over the right housing to quickly lower the volume of your music and hear ambient sounds and conversations around. Cascaded down from 1000X series, the SENSE ENGINE gives users the power to tune in and out of music at a touch. Headphones comes with touch control and lets you swipe the touchpad on the right earcup to play, pause, go back, skip songs and adjust the volume, making them perfect for use on the go. With a huge 30 hours of battery life, the headphones sustain enough power to accompany you. Now enjoy music and immerse yourself in your favourite tune’s day in and day out. The top it up, headphones comes with quick charge function that provides up to one hour of wireless playback after just ten minutes of charging. Now it’s even easier to get the party started with just your voice. With built-in Google Assistant & Amazon Alexa, use your voice to ask for your favourite tune, change the volume and enjoy hands-free, voice-controlled experience. All you need to do is ask your preferred voice assistant to play your favourite tracks, effortlessly

P_Description: Level U is the perfect choice for a comfortable listening experience on the go. These in-ear wireless Bluetooth headphones give you crisp sound quality on music as well as phone calls. Its highly ergonomic and stylish design fits comfortably around your neck and lets you enjoy your music hustle free. Performance The Level U Bluetooth device gives 10Hrs of music play time, 11Hrs of talk time and 500Hrs of standby on its built-in Lithium-ion battery. It supports a micro USB charging cable and is compatible with all Bluetooth enabled devices. Comfort These wireless headsets are ergonomically designed to fit around your neck and feature a flexible urethane joint that enables you to wear it for long periods of time comfortably. The earbuds come with stabilising gels for an in-ear comfort and perfect fit for long term use. Its intuitive button designs make it easy to control volume, play, pause and track advance. Quality sound These bluetooth earphones have a large 12mm speaker which deliver clear, high-quality sound. It also features dual microphone noise reduction and echo cancellation. The dedicated sound app on your paired Android device gives you advanced sound settings for an enhanced sound experience. Ergonomic Design With an extremely comfortable fit along with a lightweight construction (33 g), the Level U in-ear wireless headphone keeps you cool in your long music sessions. It also comes with ergonomically designed hybrid-type ear tips adjustable to all neck sizes. Flaunt your personal style statement, with Level U that features a stylish accessory like design. P_Description: The WH-CH710N, Wireless Noise Cancelling Headphones offer powerful, distraction-free listening wherever you are. With Noise Cancelling via Dual Noise Sensor Technology, as well as Ambient Sound mode, you can take control of what you hear and with 35 hours of wireless playback, you can listen to music all day long. Whether you're taking a long-haul flight or commuting to work, the Automatic Artificial Intelligence Noise Cancelling function (AINC) constantly analyses environmental ambient sound components, and automatically selects the most effective noise cancelling filter for your surroundings. Dual microphones feeding forwards and backwards mean the headphones catch more ambient sounds than ever before. So, whether you're trying to block out city traffic or office chatter, you'll be able to get completely lost in whatever you're listening to. Ambient Sound mode puts you in complete control of your listening experience. Switch it on, and you'll be able to listen to your music, while still hearing the essential everyday sounds that keep you safe, like traffic noise and transport announcements. A built-in Li-ion battery means that you can listen to up to 35 hours of audio on a single charge. Plus, with quick charging, you get 60 minutes of playback from just 10 minutes of charging. The headphones have a sleek, rounded design that looks as good as they sound. The new 30-mm drivers achieve a pure, clear sound even with light and comfortable headphones, ideal for reproducing a range of frequencies, from low beats to high vocals. A simple button press connects you to your smartphone's Voice Assistant to get directions, play music and communicate with contacts.

P_Description: Boom Buds are a set of Truly Wireless Stereo Earbuds by Boom Audio. These earbuds are an amalgamation of carefully crafted acoustics and bleeding edge consumer technology.  The latest Bluetooth 5.0 (10M wireless range) makes sure that the connection never drops during those important calls or your favourite songs. It also ensures that you get an incredible sound quality with deep bass, balanced mids and clear highs.  Boom Buds ergonomic design and light weight makes it a perfect pick as your daily driver earbuds. They fit securely and stay firmly in place even when you are working out or running. They come with an IPX4 sweat proof rating, so you don’t have to worry about them during your hardest training sessions.  The earbuds can last up to 3.5 hours continuously on a single charge. The 350mAh battery case provides an extra 9+ hours of battery, so that you have access to you music all day. They come with a built-in Active Voice Assistant, which allows you to call Siri on the move and without pressing a single button. Just activate it and say “Hey Siri”. Boom Earbuds are designed for the new generation of music lover and can be carried anywhere, thanks to its compact and light weight design.  Boom Earbuds come with a 1-year warranty from the manufacturer from the date of purchase by the end consumer.

P_Description: Jabra Elite 75t offer a great calls and music experience, engineered for comfort and tested for secure fit. You can be confident that they’ll stay put, And the smaller, ergonomic new design means they’re also comfortable. With enhanced 4-microphone call technology, you can be sure of great quality for your calls. Wherever you are, the earbuds’ 4 microphones actively work to filter out disruptive noise and amplify your voice, so your calls sound crystal clear, even in noisy or windy environments like the street or train stations. Get up to 7.5 hours on a single charge, with the handy charging case giving you up to a total of 28 hours. Fast charging allows you to get up to an hour of battery in just 15 minutes. Your music tastes are as individual as you are, which is why the Jabra Elite 75t come with a customizable equalizer; just download the Jabra Sound+ app, and set your levels according to your preferences. Whether you prefer to boost the bass or turn up the treble, you can be sure that your music will always sound exactly the way you want it to. And thanks to the proven true wireless connection, your music – or your calls – won’t be interrupted by audio dropouts or interference. The Jabra Elite 75t comes with rock-solid 4th generation true wireless technology. With an IP55 rating, and an extended 2-year warranty for protection against dust and water damage, you can be assured that your earbuds are durable enough for day-to-day Wear. Jabra Elite 75t also comes with one-touch access to your voice assistant of choice, including Siri or Google Assistant, allowing you to easily stay connected to your digital world.

P_Description: Treks Titanium open-ear wireless bone-conduction headphones are the smart alternative to traditional in-ear sport headphones and earbuds because they let you keep your ears open so you can hear surrounding sounds. Bone conduction technology, an open ear design and a suite of audio features deliver premium music play and crystal clear calling promise. Designed with athletes in mind, treks titanium are sweat proof, secure, and will allow you to hear your surroundings - no matter where life takes you. With leaks layer technology that significantly reduces natural sound leakage, these headphones are ip55 certified to repel sweat, dust and moisture, from workouts to wicked weather. Enjoy six hours of continuous music and calls on a single charge while eq presents boost bass and reduce vibration on the go. Dual noise cancelling microphones exclude surrounding noise, effectively enhancing speech. Audrey says voice prompts guide users through power, pair, play and talk. Aftershocks bone-conduction technology your music and your surroundings. Bone conduction is a natural part of the hearing process--sound travels through our eardrums and bones simultaneously. We've taken the concept to the next level through development of a suite of proprietary audio technologies and design patents. The result is headphones that deliver unrivalled situational awareness fort. How they work: transducers guide mini vibrations through the cheekbones to the inner ears, delivering sound without plugging or covering them. You hear your music like never before. (don't worry, only you'll be able to hear it. ) and you'll also be able to hear more of the sounds around you (think cars and people calling for you). Included in the box: headphones, carrying case, micro-usb charger, ear plugs, and fit bands. Hassle-free 2-year warranty.

P_Description: In your world, superior sound is essential, so slip on a pair of JBL LIVE500BT wireless around-ear headphones. Equipped with massive 50mm drivers, JBL LIVE500BT headphones deliver JBL Signature Sound punctuated with enhanced bass so every track on every playlist pops. Need some help getting through the day? Easily access the Amazon Alexa with a tap on the ear cup and play your favorite playlist, text your friend or check the weather and much more, without glancing at your phone. But that’s not all. The JBL LIVE500BT headphones can also keep you in touch with your surroundings thanks to the Ambient Aware function and TalkThru Technology letting you have a conversation without removing the headphones. Lightweight and comfortable thanks to the pillow soft padded headband, you’ll enjoy 30 hours of music streaming with 2 hours of recharging time, multi-point connection capabilities and a convenient detachable cable with remote/mic, that lets you rock on even when the battery goes off. Rock out while staying tuned in with the JBL LIVE500BT headphones.

P_Description: With 4 dynamic drivers, PTron BT Boom dual driver earphones offer best-in-class 3 hours of non-stop music playtime or talk-time on a single full charge. Let the music accompany wherever you go. Latest Bluetooth 5.0 technology, PTron BT Boom in-ear wireless headphones offer incredible high fidelity stereo sound quality with bass and crystal clear treble. Four dynamic drivers in total combining with PU+PEEK composite diaphragm design deliver the best low-frequency sound, clear vocals, and Hi-Res high-frequency up to 20Khz. With ergonomic lightweight design and silicone ear caps, these Bluetooth headphones are secure in your ears and rest comfortably in the ear canal to guarantee fatigue-free and tangle free comfort. Advanced Bluetooth chipset ensures seamless wireless connectivity within the range of 10 meters (33ft) low battery consumption and fast pairing. These wireless earphones with built-in HD microphone ensure a hands-free call experience. Just press the multi-function buttons on the in-line remote control to manage a music playlist or phone call. Other specifications: Charging input DC 5V, micro USB charging port, 1.5 hours charging time.

P_Description: The WF-SP800N truly wireless sports headphones combine long battery life, resistance to water and sweat and deep bass sound with digital noise cancelling. So, when the going gets tough, they won't let you down. With an IP55 rating, splashes, sweat and dust won't stop these water-resistant headphones or your workout. You can even rinse them after a tough training session. At full charge, the headphones offer up to 9 hours of power, while the handy charging case provides an extra 9 hours. That's up to 18 hours of noise-free listening. With noise-cancelling switched off, it's even longer 13 hours of power on a full charge, with an extra 13 hours provided by the charging case, for up to 26 hours of play time. if you're in a hurry, 10 minutes' quick charging gives you up to 60 minutes of music playback with noise cancelling. A Bluetooth chip, which transmits sound to left and right ears simultaneously, coupled with optimized antenna design ensures a stable connection and outstanding listening. Low audio latency makes for enjoyable viewing too. The compact charging case not only protects your WF-SP800N, it also lets you power up on the go. Holding a single further full charge, the case lets you enjoy up to 18 hours of music playback with noise cancelling switched on and up to 26 hours without. Quick charging is also available. When you need that special playlist to take your workout to the next level, noise cancelling blocks out distractions, like the sounds of the gym or the street, so it's just you and the beat. The WF-SP800N delivers clearer voice quality for hands-free calling and you can take calls using either or both, of the earbuds. This allows you to alternate their recharging or hear calls more clearly in noisy environments.
